name: search_result
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool location_v2.
Tool description: We are providing a location search result according to your search query
API description: Fetches location search results based on a search query and optional latitude and longitude parameters.

latitude.description: Latitude to refine the search query. Defaults to '24.562394'.

longitude.description: Longitude to refine the search query. Defaults to '73.7124675'.
